In motorsport, Danica Patrick becomes the first woman to win pole position at the Daytona 500 and the NASCAR Sprint Cup Series. (AP via ESPN) (CNN)Europol announces that a total of 680 football matches are under investigation for match fixing. Of these, 380 are in Europe, including World Cup and European Championship qualifying matches as well as Champions League matches in England. (CNN) (BBC) (ESPN) (The Guardian)